name: RateGenie
0:
”Alexa, ask Rate Genie what the current fed rate is”
”Alexa, ask Rate Genie what the current thirty year fixed mortgage rate is”
”Alexa, ask Rate Genie what the fed is going to do”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rate genie
des: Rate Genie allows you to quickly get interest rate information for a variety of products like a thirty year fixed mortgage, fifteen year fixed mortgage, five year ARM, and the overall Fed rate. In addition Rate Genie can make predictions as to whether the Fed is going to increase or lower rates based on the current six month trend(s).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
